    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长抛弃民主党初选，寻求独立竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四面楚歌的纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）将放弃民主党初选，并作为一个独立竞选，并为一场比赛增加了另一个转折，该比赛上个月被前任州长安德鲁·库莫（Andrew Cuomo）的入口颠覆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利退出ICC，因为内塔尼亚胡在访问期间违反了逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利宣布退出国际刑事法院，总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）在布达佩斯（Budapest）接待了本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu），无视以色列领导人的逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
